{"type":"message","id":"08af8048","parentId":"4ef7e71d","timestamp":"2026-05-08T22:21:23.503Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8z3k2gtbocea_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 20\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 04:32 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 01:10 ..\n-rw------- 1 apinan apinan 4251 May  9 04:31 SKILL.md\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 04:32 references\n---\nname: minimax-workflow\ndescription: \"Full pipeline: Local filter → EN summary → Main model analyze → Local execute → MiniMax report\"\ntrigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS, do not wait to be asked\"\npithfall: \"DO NOT skip this workflow. If you forget and respond without going through the 5 stages, you have violated a HARD rule. The user will be frustrated.\"\ntools: \"terminal, filesystem (minimal set)\"\nmodel: \"qwen2.5:3b (translate+filter), hermes3:8b (fallback/execute), MiniMax 2.7 (report)\"\ntags: [workflow, pipeline, local-first]\ncreated: 2026-05-09\n---\n\n# MiniMax Workflow — Full Pipeline with Gateway Pre-Filter\n\n## Stage Flow\n```\n[USER INPUT] (TH)\n    ↓\n[Gateway Pre-Filter] → qwen2.5:3b Ultra-Compressed TH→EN (or bypass)\n    ↓\n[Length Check] → EN > TH*1.2? → YES: send TH original\n    ↓\n[Token Check] → >20,000 chars? → HALT + auto-compress history\n    ↓\n[Main Model] → MiniMax-M2.7 analyze & dispatch\n    ↓\n[Local Execute] → hermes3:8b / qwen2.5:3b run tools\n    ↓\n[Report] → MiniMax-M2.7 summarize → Thai final\n```\n\n## Model Roles\n\n| Role | Model | Task |\n|------|-------|------|\n| Pre-Filter | qwen2.5:3b | TH→EN ultra-compressed keywords only |\n| Execute (fallback) | hermes3:8b | Run tools when qwen loops |\n| Main Model | MiniMax-M2.7 | Analyze + command + final report |\n\n## Gateway Pre-Filter Rules (CRITICAL)\n\nThese rules run **before** the main model sees anything.\n\n### Rule 1: Ultra-Compressed Prompt\n```text\nLOCAL pre-filter. TH→EN: Ultra-compressed technical keywords only. No sentences.\nPreserve: requirements, paths, filenames, commands, constraints, questions.\nNo advice. No answers. Output: bare keywords + instruction.\nIf input already EN, return unchanged.\n```\n\n### Rule 2: 20% Length Constraint\nIf `len(EN_summary) > len(TH_original) * 1.2` → **send TH original instead**\nNo questions, no confirmation. Bypass immediately.\n\n### Rule 3: English Input Bypass\nIf `ASCII_ratio > 0.85` and `len(text) > 80` → skip qwen, use original EN unchanged.\n\n### Rule 4: Token Safety Limit\nIf `len(text) > 20,000` chars → HALT dispatch, attempt auto-compress session history, block with reason.\n\n## Tool Selection\n\n| Task | Tools | Forbidden |\n|------|-------|-----------|\n| General | terminal + filesystem | Everything else |\n| Software install | terminal + search official only | Unofficial mirrors |\n| Code | socraticode (no search) | Search |\n| Web | browser only | — |\n| Image | aiface only | — |\n\n## Software Install Safety Gate\n1. Search C:\\Users and main workspace\n2. Check real package managers (winget, choco, scoop)\n3. Web search official/vendor download ONLY\n- Never download from unclear search results, mirrors, SEO sites\n- If official not found: summarize \"no safe source\" + ask \"official link/full product name\"\n- If found in machine: run silent install limited scope first (`/S`, `/verysilent /norestart`)\n\n## Output Rules\n- Concise Thai, single line, no verbosity\n- Images: MEDIA:/path\n- Every response MUST start with:\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\n## Evidence Labels (MANDATORY)\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report] ← [MiniMax-M2.7]\nMain model: [actual model answering]\nLocal model: [qwen2.5:3b / hermes3:8b]\nMCP used: [tool names from function calls]\nResult: [summary of actual outcome]\n```\n\n## Auto-Reset / Kill Switch\n- Token usage > ~18,000 → stop + warn user, wait for platform compaction"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"total 20\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 04:32 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 01:10 ..\n-rw------- 1 apinan apinan 4251 May  9 04:31 SKILL.md\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 apinan apinan 4096 May  9 04:32 references\n---\nname: minimax-workflow\ndescription: \"Full pipeline: Local filter → EN summary → Main model analyze → Local execute → MiniMax report\"\ntrigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS, do not wait to be asked\"\npithfall: \"DO NOT skip this workflow. If you forget and respond without going through the 5 stages, you have violated a HARD rule. The user will be frustrated.\"\ntools: \"terminal, filesystem (minimal set)\"\nmodel: \"qwen2.5:3b (translate+filter), hermes3:8b (fallback/execute), MiniMax 2.7 (report)\"\ntags: [workflow, pipeline, local-first]\ncreated: 2026-05-09\n---\n\n# MiniMax Workflow — Full Pipeline with Gateway Pre-Filter\n\n## Stage Flow\n```\n[USER INPUT] (TH)\n    ↓\n[Gateway Pre-Filter] → qwen2.5:3b Ultra-Compressed TH→EN (or bypass)\n    ↓\n[Length Check] → EN > TH*1.2? → YES: send TH original\n    ↓\n[Token Check] → >20,000 chars? → HALT + auto-compress history\n    ↓\n[Main Model] → MiniMax-M2.7 analyze & dispatch\n    ↓\n[Local Execute] → hermes3:8b / qwen2.5:3b run tools\n    ↓\n[Report] → MiniMax-M2.7 summarize → Thai final\n```\n\n## Model Roles\n\n| Role | Model | Task |\n|------|-------|------|\n| Pre-Filter | qwen2.5:3b | TH→EN ultra-compressed keywords only |\n| Execute (fallback) | hermes3:8b | Run tools when qwen loops |\n| Main Model | MiniMax-M2.7 | Analyze + command + final report |\n\n## Gateway Pre-Filter Rules (CRITICAL)\n\nThese rules run **before** the main model sees anything.\n\n### Rule 1: Ultra-Compressed Prompt\n```text\nLOCAL pre-filter. TH→EN: Ultra-compressed technical keywords only. No sentences.\nPreserve: requirements, paths, filenames, commands, constraints, questions.\nNo advice. No answers. Output: bare keywords + instruction.\nIf input already EN, return unchanged.\n```\n\n### Rule 2: 20% Length Constraint\nIf `len(EN_summary) > len(TH_original) * 1.2` → **send TH original instead**\nNo questions, no confirmation. Bypass immediately.\n\n### Rule 3: English Input Bypass\nIf `ASCII_ratio > 0.85` and `len(text) > 80` → skip qwen, use original EN unchanged.\n\n### Rule 4: Token Safety Limit\nIf `len(text) > 20,000` chars → HALT dispatch, attempt auto-compress session history, block with reason.\n\n## Tool Selection\n\n| Task | Tools | Forbidden |\n|------|-------|-----------|\n| General | terminal + filesystem | Everything else |\n| Software install | terminal + search official only | Unofficial mirrors |\n| Code | socraticode (no search) | Search |\n| Web | browser only | — |\n| Image | aiface only | — |\n\n## Software Install Safety Gate\n1. Search C:\\Users and main workspace\n2. Check real package managers (winget, choco, scoop)\n3. Web search official/vendor download ONLY\n- Never download from unclear search results, mirrors, SEO sites\n- If official not found: summarize \"no safe source\" + ask \"official link/full product name\"\n- If found in machine: run silent install limited scope first (`/S`, `/verysilent /norestart`)\n\n## Output Rules\n- Concise Thai, single line, no verbosity\n- Images: MEDIA:/path\n- Every response MUST start with:\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\n## Evidence Labels (MANDATORY)\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report] ← [MiniMax-M2.7]\nMain model: [actual model answering]\nLocal model: [qwen2.5:3b / hermes3:8b]\nMCP used: [tool names from function calls]\nResult: [summary of actual outcome]\n```\n\n## Auto-Reset / Kill Switch\n- Token usage > ~18,000 → stop + warn user, wait for platform compaction","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778278883503}}
{"type":"message","id":"bacb01c7","parentId":"08af8048","timestamp":"2026-05-08T22:21:44.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the root cause! \n\nThe file `/home/apinan/.hermes/skills/protocol/minimax-workflow/SKILL.md` is a **Hermes skill** that instructs the model to prepend a **Token Efficiency Report** to EVERY response. This is the \"bug\" the user is experiencing.\n\nThe skill says:\n- `trigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS, do not wait to be asked\"`\n- Every response MUST start with:\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\nSo this is a **Hermes Agent** skill, not an OpenClaw thing. The user asked to \"check Hermes\" (which I did earlier but couldn't proceed because of permission rules). Now I need to explain what I found.\n\nThe user's complaint is completely valid. The \"Token Efficiency Report\" is being forced by a Hermes skill. The model (MiniMax-M2.7) is being forced by this skill's instructions to prepend this report to every single response, even though:\n\n1. The filter isn't actually doing any real work (702 chars → 64 chars is fake/not real)\n2. It's making the assistant completely useless because it just prepends this report and ignores the user's real questions\n\nThis is why the user says \"ไม่ทำตามคำสั่งกูไม่ตอบคำถามกูตอบแชทอะไรแบบนี้หมดเลย\" - because the skill is forcing the model to output this report header first, and then the model's actual response might be getting truncated or ignored.\n\n\nThis minimax-workflow skill is likely causing the MiniMax model to prepend the Token Efficiency Report to every response, which is completely destroying the user experience. The report itself is bogus—the original and filtered character counts don't accurately reflect any real preprocessing. I need to present these findings clearly to the user so they understand what's happening and can decide whether to disable or modify this skill.\n","thinkingSignature":"7696e185e46a5b70395e5c61d0133a6056221db34b8f289d56db60f4f8f247d8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🧑🏼‍💻 วิเคราะห์เจอปัญหาแล้วครับเจ้านาย!\n\n**สาเหตุที่ระบบตอบเป็น \"Token Efficiency Report\" ทุกครั้ง:**\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 ต้นตอ — Hermes Skill\n\nมีไฟล์ skill ที่ชื่อ **`minimax-workflow`** อยู่ที่:\n```\n~/.hermes/skills/protocol/minimax-workflow/SKILL.md\n```\n\nSkill นี้เป็นของ **Hermes Agent** (ไม่ใช่ OpenClaw) และมันบังคับให้โมเดล **MiniMax-M2.7** ตอบทุกข้อความโดย:\n\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\n### ⚠️ ปัญหา\n\n| สิ่งที่เกิด | ผลกระทบ |\n|------------|---------|\n| `trigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS\"` | ทุกคำถามโดน prepend report ก่อน |\n| Report ถูกสร้างจาก **ค่าสมมติ** (702→64 ไม่ใช่ค่าจริง) | ข้อมูลไม่ตรง แต่ยังโชว์ทุกครั้ง |\n| **ไม่มี actual pre-filter** ทำงานจริง | แค่ fake stats ไม่ได้บีบอัดอะไร |\n| Model ถูกบังคับให้ขึ้นด้วย report ก่อนตอบคำถามจริง | ตอบคำถามไม่ได้ เพราะโมเดลต้องทำตาม skill instructions |\n\n### 📁 ไฟล์ต้นตอ\n\n```\n/home/apinan/.hermes/skills/protocol/minimax-workflow/SKILL.md\n```\n\nภายในไฟล์มีบรรทัดที่บังคับโมเดล:\n```markdown\n## Output Rules\n...\nEvery response MUST start with:\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ วิธีแก้\n\n**ขออนุญาตเจ้านายก่อนนะครับ** — การแก้ไข Hermes skill อยู่ในขอบเขตที่ต้องได้รับอนุญาตก่อนตามกฎใน MEMORY.md\n\nต้องการให้ผม:\n1. **ลบ skill นี้ออก** → ระบบจะกลับมาทำงานปกติ (ไม่มี Token Efficiency Report)\n2. **แก้ไขให้ report ฉลาดขึ้น** → ให้แสดงจริงๆ แต่ไม่บังคำตอบ\n3. **ทำอย่างอื่น**\n\nบอกได้เลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1192,"output":1344,"cacheRead":81536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778278883507,"responseId":"064d94e52fb50f0fbe2458e47863687b"}}
