{"type":"message","id":"3e2b4a7c","parentId":"bc9a5781","timestamp":"2026-05-08T22:22:16.592Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9ym98fkkpjg7_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: minimax-workflow\ndescription: \"Full pipeline: Local filter → EN summary → Main model analyze → Local execute → MiniMax report\"\ntrigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS, do not wait to be asked\"\npithfall: \"DO NOT skip this workflow. If you forget and respond without going through the 5 stages, you have violated a HARD rule. The user will be frustrated.\"\ntools: \"terminal, filesystem (minimal set)\"\nmodel: \"qwen2.5:3b (translate+filter), hermes3:8b (fallback/execute), MiniMax 2.7 (report)\"\ntags: [workflow, pipeline, local-first]\ncreated: 2026-05-09\n---\n\n# MiniMax Workflow — Full Pipeline with Gateway Pre-Filter\n\n## Stage Flow\n```\n[USER INPUT] (TH)\n    ↓\n[Gateway Pre-Filter] → qwen2.5:3b Ultra-Compressed TH→EN (or bypass)\n    ↓\n[Length Check] → EN > TH*1.2? → YES: send TH original\n    ↓\n[Token Check] → >20,000 chars? → HALT + auto-compress history\n    ↓\n[Main Model] → MiniMax-M2.7 analyze & dispatch\n    ↓\n[Local Execute] → hermes3:8b / qwen2.5:3b run tools\n    ↓\n[Report] → MiniMax-M2.7 summarize → Thai final\n```\n\n## Model Roles\n\n| Role | Model | Task |\n|------|-------|------|\n| Pre-Filter | qwen2.5:3b | TH→EN ultra-compressed keywords only |\n| Execute (fallback) | hermes3:8b | Run tools when qwen loops |\n| Main Model | MiniMax-M2.7 | Analyze + command + final report |\n\n## Gateway Pre-Filter Rules (CRITICAL)\n\nThese rules run **before** the main model sees anything.\n\n### Rule 1: Ultra-Compressed Prompt\n```text\nLOCAL pre-filter. TH→EN: Ultra-compressed technical keywords only. No sentences.\nPreserve: requirements, paths, filenames, commands, constraints, questions.\nNo advice. No answers. Output: bare keywords + instruction.\nIf input already EN, return unchanged.\n```\n\n### Rule 2: 20% Length Constraint\nIf `len(EN_summary) > len(TH_original) * 1.2` → **send TH original instead**\nNo questions, no confirmation. Bypass immediately.\n\n### Rule 3: English Input Bypass\nIf `ASCII_ratio > 0.85` and `len(text) > 80` → skip qwen, use original EN unchanged.\n\n### Rule 4: Token Safety Limit\nIf `len(text) > 20,000` chars → HALT dispatch, attempt auto-compress session history, block with reason.\n\n## Tool Selection\n\n| Task | Tools | Forbidden |\n|------|-------|-----------|\n| General | terminal + filesystem | Everything else |\n| Software install | terminal + search official only | Unofficial mirrors |\n| Code | socraticode (no search) | Search |\n| Web | browser only | — |\n| Image | aiface only | — |\n\n## Software Install Safety Gate\n1. Search C:\\Users and main workspace\n2. Check real package managers (winget, choco, scoop)\n3. Web search official/vendor download ONLY\n- Never download from unclear search results, mirrors, SEO sites\n- If official not found: summarize \"no safe source\" + ask \"official link/full product name\"\n- If found in machine: run silent install limited scope first (`/S`, `/verysilent /norestart`)\n\n## Output Rules\n- Concise Thai, single line, no verbosity\n- Images: MEDIA:/path\n- Every response MUST start with:\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report]\n- Original Input: [chars]\n- Filtered Input: [chars/tokens]\n- Status: [✓ or ✗]\n```\n\n## Evidence Labels (MANDATORY)\n```\n[📊 Token Efficiency Report] ← [MiniMax-M2.7]\nMain model: [actual model answering]\nLocal model: [qwen2.5:3b / hermes3:8b]\nMCP used: [tool names from function calls]\nResult: [summary of actual outcome]\n```\n\n## Auto-Reset / Kill Switch\n- Token usage > ~18,000 → stop + warn user, wait for platform compaction\n- Gateway restart required after any pre-filter code change\n\n## Memory vs Skill\n- Memory: User-specific data (name, ID, preferences) only\n- Skill: Full rules, examples, prohibitions, workflow steps\n- Rule: Every rule update → update BOTH memory AND skill\n\n## Related Skills\n| Topic | Use skill_view on |\n|-------|-------------------|\n| MCP routing | mcp-full-performance-router |\n| Code workflow | socraticode-codework-gate |\n| Local execution | local-hermes-real-execution |\n| Kill switch | real-runtime-evidence-protocol |\n| Token saving | token-saving-workflow |\n| OpenClaw safety | openclaw |\n| Pre-flight check | preflight-codework-check |\n\n## References\n- `references/gateway-pre-filter.md` — Ultra-compressed prompt + 20% rule + bypass logic"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":78,"aggregated":"---\nname: minimax-workflow\ndescription: \"Full pipeline: Local filter → EN summary → Main model analyze → Local execute → MiniMax report\"\ntrigger: \"every single user message — NO EXCEPTIONS, do not wait to be asked\"\npithfall: \"DO NOT skip this workflow. If you forget and respond without going through the 5 stages, you have violated a HARD rule. The user will be frustrated.\"\ntools: \"terminal, filesystem (minimal set)\"\nmodel: \"qwen2.5:3b (translate+filter), hermes3:8b (fallback/execute), MiniMax 2.7 (report)\"\ntags: [workflow, pipeline, local-first]\ncreated: 2026-05-09\n---\n\n# MiniMax Workflow — Full Pipeline with Gateway Pre-Filter\n\n## Stage Flow\n```\n[USER INPUT] (TH)\n    ↓\n[Gateway Pre-Filter] → qwen2.5:3b Ultra-Compressed TH→EN (or bypass)\n    ↓\n[Length Check] → EN > TH*1.2? → YES: send TH original\n    ↓\n[Token Check] → >20,000 chars? → HALT + auto-compress history\n    ↓\n[Main Model] → MiniMax-M2.7 analyze & dispatch\n    ↓\n[Local Execute] → hermes3:8b / qwen2.5:3b run tools\n    ↓\n[Report] → MiniMax-M2.7 summarize → Thai final\n```\n\n## Model Roles\n\n| Role | Model | Task |\n|------|-------|------|\n| Pre-Filter | qwen2.5:3b | TH→EN ultra-compressed keywords only |\n| Execute (fallback) | hermes3:8b | Run tools when qwen loops |\n| Main Model | MiniMax-M2.7 | Analyze + command + final report |\n\n## Gateway Pre-Filter Rules (CRITICAL