{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"8013\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-09 16:53 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"c565aa89","parentId":"96fec1c6","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:54:00.690Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"63158bad","parentId":"c565aa89","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:54:50.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why the system is not working properly. They said \"1234\" but it answered with something weird instead of working properly.\n\nLet me trace through what happens when a simple message like \"1234\" comes in:\n\n1. Message arrives at Hermes gateway\n2. Gateway emits `agent:start` hook\n3. Hook fires `minimax-bridge/handler.py`\n4. Handler runs `universal_bridge.py` with the message\n5. Bridge script outputs a full 4-UNIT report to stdout\n6. Hook sets `_bridge_done=True` and `_bridge_result=proc.stdout.strip()`\n7. Gateway sees `_bridge_done` → skips agent → returns `_bridge_result` as response\n8. User sees the full 4-UNIT report instead of the actual answer\n\nSo the problem is:\n- Hook always runs bridge for every non-\"/\" message\n- Hook sets `_bridge_result` to the FULL stdout (entire 4-UNIT report)\n- Gateway skips agent and returns this full report as the response\n\nThe user said \"1234\" and got the 4-UNIT report instead of an answer about \"1234\".\n\nThe fix needs to be in one of these places:\n1. Hook: Make it bypass for simple messages (not run bridge)\n2. Hook: Only set `_bridge_result` to the UNIT 4 summary, not the full report\n3. Gateway: Something else\n\nLooking at the hook code:\n```python\nif message.startswith(\"_\") or message.startswith(\"/\"):\n    return\n```\n\nThis skips \"/\" commands but not regular text. So \"1234\" runs through bridge.\n\nAnd the hook sets:\n```python\ncontext[\"_bridge_result\"] = result  # full stdout\ncontext[\"_bridge_done\"] = True\n```\n\nSo the full 4-UNIT report is returned.\n\nThe user wants the system to work properly. Let me explain the problem clearly and ask what they want.\n","thinkingSignature":"eb548d8441c23f385352ea08a95592007e26409c04f5dd047fb3445244b32c4e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🧑🏼‍💻 อธิบายปัญหาแบบตรงๆ\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 ทำไม \"1234\" ถึงได้ 4-UNIT Report\n\n**Flow ที่เกิดขึ้น:**\n\n```\n1. User พิมพ์ \"1234\" ไป Hermes\n       ↓\n2. Gateway emit \"agent:start\" hook\n       ↓\n3. Hook [minimax-bridge] รัน script → python universal_bridge.py \"1234\"\n       ↓\n4. Script output มาทั้งหมด (4-UNIT report เต็มๆ):\n   ═══════════════════════════════════════════\n   🚀 4-UNIT BRIDGE + SELF-HEALING\n   📥 INPUT: 1234\n   🟢 UNIT 1 ✅ → [TH→EN]\n   🔵 UNIT 2 ✅ Plan: \"1234\"\n   🟡 UNIT 3 ✅ echo \"1234\"\n   🟣 UNIT 4 ✅ สำเร็จแล้ว\n   ═══════════════════════════════════════════\n       ↓\n5. Hook เอา output ทั้งด้ามใส่ _bridge_result\n       ↓\n6. Gateway เห็น _bridge_done=True → SKIP AGENT\n       ↓\n7. ส่ง _bridge_result (4-UNIT report) กลับไป Telegram\n       ↓\n8. User เห็น: 4-UNIT report แทนคำตอบ \"1234\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ ปัญหา 2 จุด\n\n| จุด | ปัญหา |\n|-----|--------|\n| **Hook** | รัน bridge ทุก message (ไม่ได้ bypass \"1234\") |\n| **Hook** | เอา output ทั้งด้ามใส่ `_bridge_result` → ส่งกลับหมด |\n| **Gateway** | เห็น `_bridge_done=True` → skip agent เลย → ไม่ถามอะไรเลย |\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 สิ่งที่ควรจะเกิด vs สิ่งที่เกิด\n\n| | ควรเกิด | ที่เกิดจริง |\n|--|---------|-----------|\n| \"1234\" | Agent ตอบ \"1234\" ตรงๆ | ได้ 4-UNIT report |\n| Hook | ควร bypass หรือส่งแค่ summary | ส่ง report เต็มๆ |\n| Gateway | ควรรู้ว่า flag คืออะไร | skip เลยโดยไม่รู้ว่าผลลัพธ์คืออะไร |\n\n---\n\n### 💬 ถามเจ้านาย\n\n**ต้องการแก้แบบไหน?**\n\n**A) ปิด Hook เลย** → Agent ทำงานปกติไม่ผ่าน bridge\n\n**B) แก้ Hook** → ให้ส่งแค่ UNIT 4 summary (\"สำเร็จ\") ไม่ใช่ report เต็มๆ\n\n**C) แก้ Gateway** → ให้ agent ยังทำงานได้แม้มี `_bridge_done` flag\n\nบอกเจ้านายเลือกอันไหน 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15396,"output":1289,"cacheRead":129920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778320440690,"responseId":"064e373baffef3eb52434cc13d176c99