response, \"messages\": [], \"api_calls\": 0}\n            else:\n                # Run the agent normally\n                agent_result = await self._run_agent(\n                    message=message_text,\n                    context_prompt=context_prompt,\n                    history=history,\n                    source=source,\n                    session_id=session_entry.session_id,\n                    session_key=session_key,\n                    run_generation=run_generation,\n                    event_message_id=event.message_id,\n                    channel_prompt=event.channel_prompt,\n                )\n\n            # Stop persistent typing indicator now that the agent is done\n            try:\n                _typing_adapter = self.adapters.get(source.platform)","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778320875257}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ae8d740","parentId":"a49f15e0","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:02:44.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full problem. Looking at the gateway code:```python\n# If bridge hook set _bridge_done → skip agent, return bridge result directly\nif hook_ctx.get(\"_bridge_done\") and hook_ctx.get(\"_bridge_result\"):\n    response = hook_ctx[\"_bridge_result\"]\n    agent_result = {\"final_response\": response, \"messages\": [], \"api_calls\": 0}else:\n    # Run the agent normally    agent_result = await self._run_agent(...)```When `_bridge_done=True`, the gateway:1. Skips running the agent entirely\n2. Returns `_bridge_result` as the final responseThe `_bridge_result` is the ENTIRE stdout from the bridge script, which includes:```\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════🚀 4-UNIT BRIDGE + SELF-HEALING\n📥 INPUT: 1234Tokens: ~1🟢 [UNIT 1] 🟢 ...\n...✅ สำเร็จแล้ว══════════════════════════════════════════════════```\n\n\nThat's the full verbose output. The user just wants the actual answer.\n\nSo the fix needs to be: extract only the UNIT 4 summary from the bridge output (\"✅ สำเร็จแล้ว\") and return that as the response, while letting the agent still run normally with the bridge context. The boss clarified they want all 4 units to execute as the agent's thinking process, not have the agent skipped entirely.\n\nLooking at the logs showing `api_calls=0`, the agent isn't running at all when `_bridge_done=True`. I need to modify the gateway to not skip the agent but instead pass the bridge result as context so the agent can formulate its own response. And the hook's current approach of sending the entire stdout as the bridge result is wrong—it should only send the final summary.\n\nThe simplest fix is to have the hook set the bridge result but let the agent continue running with that context, so it can decide what to respond rather than just echoing the full output. The boss's clarification about running all 4 units means the agent needs to be in the loop. I should modify the gateway logic to pass the bridge result as context to the agent instead of skipping it entirely, then update the hook to send only the summary portion to keep the message concise.","thinkingSignature":"c86147fb0f928d7c77f3b1edb67b8745b6ba74e9889432e60e7510404c56927e"},{"type":"text","text":"เข้าใจปัญหาแล้วครับ!\n\n**ปัญหาต้นตอ:**\n\n1. **Hook** รัน bridge แล้วเอา stdout เต็มๆ (ทั้ง report + UNIT logs) ใส่ `_bridge_result`\n2. **Gateway** เห็น `_bridge_done=True` → **skip agent เลย** → ไม่ได้ให้ agent คิด/ตอบ\n3. **Result** ที่ส่งกลับ = stdout เต็มๆ ที่รวม UNIT labels ทั้งหมด\n\n**Boss ต้องการ:** รัน 4 UNIT เต็มๆ แล้วให้ **agent ตอบ** ไม่ใช่ skip agent\n\n---\n\n**สรุป 2 จุดที่ต้องแก้:**\n\n| จุด | แก้ยังไง |\n|-----|-----------|\n| **Gateway** | `_bridge_done=True` → ไม่ skip agent แต่ส่ง `_bridge_result` เป็น context ให้ agent คิดต่อ |\n| **Hook** | ส่งแค่ UNIT 4 summary เป็น `_bridge_result` (ไม่ใช่ stdout เต็มๆ) |\n\n---\n\nรอเจ้านายบอก confirm ก่อนแก้ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116585,"output":862,"cacheRead":34283,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778320875269,"responseId":"064e38eddbdb9f46b2873b1e6f08e8cc"}}
